<sect2>
<title>Introduction to <application><acronym>GPM</acronym></application></title>

<para>The <application><acronym>GPM</acronym></application> package contains a 
mouse server for the console and <command>xterm</command>. This is useful for 
cutting and pasting text in console mode, and also because many console-based 
programs need it to compile mouse support into themselves.</para>

